{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1431637, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 280730, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "符合", "timestamp": 1618121221, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1431646, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 280730, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "太符合了", "timestamp": 1618121289, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1431658, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 280730, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "符合，其中有符号价值", "timestamp": 1618121359, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1431693, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 280730, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 正经提问，有什么规律普通商品符合但是奢侈品不符合的吗？用以区分二者", "timestamp": 1618121583, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1431701, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 280730, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 需求价格弹性", "timestamp": 1618121636, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1431775, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 280730, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 普通商品能通过低价获得竞争力，争取市场，打败对手。而奢侈品低价会贬损品牌竞争力，失去市场。普通商品卖的是商品的使用价值，而奢侈品卖的是附着在商品上的虚荣或者地位认同。", "timestamp": 1618122300, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1431816, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 280730, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "把奢侈品想象成一种证书，能买得起这个证书就证明了自己的购买力。它的价值除了本身的实物价值外，还包含了作为信号传递媒介的价值。", "timestamp": 1618122633, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1431834, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 280730, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "毕竟现实生活中信息获取和传递都是有成本的，而马克思的模型中将信息成本抽象为零，因此用劳动价值论不太能解释信息传递媒介的价值。", "timestamp": 1618122734, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1432177, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 280730, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 谢谢大神！", "timestamp": 1618126017, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1432209, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 280730, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 奢侈品（以服装为代表）使用价值高不高？想弄清楚使用价值的意思。我想表达的是奢侈品不具备和价格匹配的实用能力，这个叫什么价值？", "timestamp": 1618126176, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1433102, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 280730, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 奢侈品的定义就是非生活必需品。其价值体现在稀缺性，提供的服务特殊性，并因此有了较高的溢价。", "timestamp": 1618134826, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 5, "pid": 280730, "reply": 11, "tag": null, "text": "奢侈品符合价值规律吗\n", "timestamp": 1618121072, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1618134829, "url": "", "vote": {}}}